<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idefa1c38c-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s303102"><num value="303102">§ 303102.</num><heading> Funding</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For each of fiscal years 2012 to 2023,<ref class="footnoteRef" idref="fn002022">1</ref><note type="footnote" id="fn002022"><num>1</num> See Application of Section note below.</note> $150,000,000 shall be deposited in the Historic Preservation Fund from revenues due and payable to the United States under section 9 of the Outer Continental Shelf Lands Act (<ref href="/us/usc/t43/s1338">43 U.S.C. 1338</ref>), <ref href="/us/usc/t10/s8733/b">section 8733(b) of title 10</ref>, or both, notwithstanding any provision of law that those proceeds shall be credited to miscellaneous receipts of the Treasury.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idefa1c38d-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db">(<ref href="/us/pl/113/287/s3">Pub. L. 113–287, § 3</ref>, <date date="2014-12-19">Dec. 19, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/3206">128 Stat. 3206</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/114/289/tVIII/s802/a">Pub. L. 114–289, title VIII, § 802(a)</ref>, (c)(1), <date date="2016-12-16">Dec. 16, 2016</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/130/1494">130 Stat. 1494</ref>, 1495; <ref href="/us/pl/115/232/dA/tVIII/s809/s">Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VIII, § 809(s)</ref>, <date date="2018-08-13">Aug. 13, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/1844">132 Stat. 1844</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
